lead_paragraph: Maria Jespersen scored a career-best 26 points and had 15 rebounds as No. 23 South Florida pulled away in the third quarter and cruised to a 74-60 victory over Stetson on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 23 South Florida Women Pull Away From Stetson, 74-60
